data.title: 'FUBAR' Season 2 release date on Netflix: Will Arnold Schwarzenegger's series release in 2024?
meta_keywords: fubar season 2 release date on netflix
data.meta_description: 'FUBAR' Season 2 featuring Arnold Schwarzenegger in the lead role, will be releasing on Netflix.
data.text:
Synopsis

'FUBAR' Season 2 featuring Arnold Schwarzenegger in the lead role, will be releasing on Netflix.

'FUBAR' Season 2 release date on Netflix is keenly awaited by show's fans and OTT streaming giant users. The Netflix Original action-comedy series was renewed during Netflix Tudum in June last year. This came after 'FUBAR' Season 1 made its mark on the viewers' ratings on the OTT streaming giant following its debut on May 25.

Arnold Schwarzenegger as Luke Brunner is returning. The filming of the Netflix show is scheduled to begin April 29 and conclude by August-end, as per a report in WhatsonNetflix.

With filming for the highly anticipated second season of FUBAR commencing between April 2024 and August 2024, viewers can expect to see the return of their favorite characters and the introduction of new storylines in either the second or third quarter of 2025, as per the report. However, there is no official confirmation in this regard.

Last week, Schwarzenegger gave a health update and shared that he will be ready to shoot for the second season of ‘Fubar’ by next month. The actor shared a picture of himself with a thank you note for those who sent him messages. Schwarzenegger went on to assure his fans that the health issues will not keep him from shooting.

Talking about 'Fubar', it revolves around a CIA operative on the verge of retirement, who discovers a family secret and is forced to go back into the field for one last job.

The series also has Monica Barbaro, Milan Carter, Gabriel Luna, Fortune Feimster, Travis Van Winkle, Fabiana Udenio, Barbara Eve Harris, Aparna Brielle, Andy Buckley and Jay Baruchel.

FAQs:

Q1. Is 'FUBAR' Season 2 happening?

A1. Yes, 'FUBAR' Season 2 is happening on Netflix.

Q2. Where can we watch 'FUBAR' Season 2?

A2. 'FUBAR' Season 2 can be watched on Netflix.
